⍝ TRANSLATION NOTE: src/core/debug.rs
⍝ Purpose: tiny debug toggles and logging helpers.
⍝ Key translation decisions: simple env-style switch emulated with integer flag.
⍝ Feature parity: PARTIAL.

◯ debug_enabled⟨flag⟩ {
    return flag == 1;
}

◯ debug_log⟨flag, msg⟩ {
    if (debug_enabled(flag)) {
        print("[debug] " + msg);
    }
    return 0;
}
